data.description: Charming three bedroom, one bath home featuring sleek laminate flooring throughout. This residence has two living areas, a cozy wood burning fireplace and a stylish kitchen with pristine white cabinets. Enjoy the convenience of a large laundry room and an impressive 20x26 shop equipped with electric and a garage door opener. The large fenced backyard offers a blank slate to create your very own outdoor living space. This home is perfect for comfortable living and versatile spaces and could make a great rental investment property.
